1. *Klinci* su bili puni energije. (The kids were full of energy.)
2. *Klinaca* je bilo puno na igralištu. (There were lots of kids at the playground.)
3. *Klincima* je trebalo malo pomoći. (The kids needed a little help.)
4. *Klince* je podigao u nebo. (He lifted the kid up to the sky.)
5. *Klincu* je bilo jako strah. (The kid was really scared.)
6. *Klincima* je bilo teško pratiti lekcije. (It was difficult for the kids to follow the lessons.)